5. employeeSchema - add a new field called as department - type is objectId,  required
                 - ensure when a new employee is added, he/she belong to a department 
6.
      GET/customers/:id - show one customer
      GET/departments/:id - show one department
      GET/employees/:id - show one employee


      delete/customers/:id - delete one customer
      delete/departments/:id- delete one department
      delete/employees/:id - delete one employee


     
      PUT/customers/:id - update the customer
      PUT/departments/:id - update the department
      PUT/employees/:id - update the employee